moderatorInfo.description: I am a moderator here, and as such, have been asked to investigate the recent accusations of wrongdoing by an associate of our own. We can be 100% confirmed that our associate was neither paid, nor involved in this case, nor did he have a relationship with the person being accused. The accuser in question has also denied any involvement and made his own allegations of wrongdoing in the past.
moderatorInfo.termsAndConditions: My terms as a moderator are to prevent a person who is not well behaved from causing a problem by being rude or by being aggressive or by being unreasonable. If you have to ask why someone has been banned, I will give it to you. If they are well-behaved, I will let them in.
